<title>INDIA: India to auction 1.5 bln rupee in t-bills on May 2.</title>
<headline>India to auction 1.5 bln rupee in t-bills on May 2.</headline>
<dateline>BOMBAY 1997-04-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Reserve Bank of India (RBI) said on Tuesday it will hold an auction of 91-day treasury bills worth 1.5 billion rupees on May 2.</p>
<p>Results of the auction will be announced the same day and payment by successful bidders will be on May 3, the RBI said in a statement.</p>
